 class HighLowKey
          HighLowKey is not used for DDL Generator
 class IdentityKey

 class MaxKey
          MaxKey is not used for DDL Generator
 class SequenceKey
          SEQUENCE key generator can be used only with Oracle, PostgreSQL, Interbase and SAP DB.

          UUIDKey is not used for DDL Generator

Classes in org.castor.ddl.schemaobject that implement SchemaObject
 class AbstractSchemaObject
          AbstractSchemaObject is the base class for Table, Field, ForeignKey, KeyGenerator...
 class Field
          Field handles informations for creating field's sql.
 class ForeignKey
          ForeignKey handle information for foreign key creation.
 class Index
          Current implemetation is not supported INDEX creation
 class KeyGenerator
          KeyGenerator is abstract class for Key generator
 class Schema
          Schema contains a set of table and schema options.
 class Table
          Table contains fields, foreignkeys, indexes and table's options
